Texts.Eng: Bring the ^green;Greenhouse^reset; to ^orange;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
Thanks so much. You are a life saver! Now I can tinker with plant life! Maybe I can figure out how to upgrade it, too!
^orange;Greenhouses^reset; are all the rage these days. I want one, but my budget can't swing it. Do you have one lying around I might use?
